IDENTIFIABLE INTANGIBLE ASSETS, GOODWILL AND UMBRO IMPAIRMENT), AND THE RETROACTIVE REINSTATEMENT OF THE RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT TAX CREDIT. THE TAX EXTENDERS AND ALTERNATIVE MINIMUM TAX RELIEF ACT OF 2008, WHICH WAS SIGNED INTO LAW DURING THE

