OUR ON-GOING EFFECTIVE TAX RATE RESULTING FROM OUR OPERATIONS OUTSIDE OF THE UNITED STATES, AS OUR TAX RATES ON THOSE OPERATIONS ARE GENERALLY LOWER THAN THE U.S. STATUTORY RATE.

